{"tid":378740,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋漫畫]有冇人記得一套關於乒乓波嘅漫畫","createTime":"2017-08-28T17:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T12:42:52.000Z","uid":65473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d82cd063ede92fe3151fb7a28fa3eda0617a564","tid":378740,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"細個睇過一套乒乓波漫畫<br />\n想追返但唔記得叫咩名<br />\n淨係記得個主角騎住電單車俾人由學校天台推咗落去<br />\n跟住俾雷擊中開咗腦<br />\n揸住部車降落咗去籃球架上面<br />\n之後主角可以睇到好多數據<br />\n例如啲波嘅路徑 女女嘅三圍<br />\n<br />\n仲記得有張波枱係有幾條龍<br />\n打場波都要爛衫爛褲嘅<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以幫下手話我知係邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1258c3712eb2a9d92d4d47a035efe71b43f825","tid":378740,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09b5105ee358aef5e2a21c754a123ad3859dca41","tid":378740,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乒乓王子?</blockquote><br />\n應該係日漫來的"},{"pid":"ffe96d7537c32c55558c853b123500ec7b94a20a","tid":378740,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"絕招係咪用扳邊去擊球？"},{"pid":"1ce862b6d9c063d6fc2240cdf0368f57a0293487","tid":378740,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕招係咪用扳邊去擊球？</blockquote><br />\n板"},{"pid":"7b0e51b35f99df4248e7a49d84d18d6b13e23c9f","tid":378740,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絕招係咪用扳邊去擊球？</blockquote><br />\n板</blockquote><br />\n好似有呢招"},{"pid":"485b0e500d949fb35b3211613940409dd4a7fe3e","tid":378740,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絕招係咪用扳邊去擊球？</blockquote><br />\n板</blockquote><br />\n好似有呢招</blockquote><br />\n好似出左3定4本單行就停戴左"},{"pid":"5b1355b9de4f8472b